This system has premium modern CLI tools. ALWAYS use these instead of traditional commands:

| Instead of | Use | Notes |
|------------|-----|-------|
| `find` | `fd` | Modern file finder |
| `ls` | `eza` | Git-aware listing |
| `cat` | `bat` | Syntax highlighting |
| `grep` | `rg` | Ripgrep (faster) |
| `du` | `dust` | Visual disk usage |
| `ps` | `procs` | Better process view |
| `top` | `btm` | Modern monitor |
| `cut/awk` | `choose` | Column extraction |

### File Type Handling
- **JSON**: `jless` (interactive) or `bat`
- **YAML**: `yq` (processing) or `bat`
- **CSV**: `csvlook` (table) or `miller`
- **Markdown**: `glow` (formatted) or `bat`
